<article id="article" class="clearfix" data-id="23980" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article">
  
    <header class="grid-prepend-four grid-twelve">
      <time content="2014-03-04T04:46:11Z" datetime="2014-03-04T04:46:11Z" itemprop="datePublished" pubdate="pubdate">March 3 2014, 11.46pm EST</time>
      <h1 class="entry-title grid-eight instapaper_title" itemprop="name">
        <span class="nobr">Black-market</span> lottery: organ donation and the international transplant&nbsp;trade
      </h1>
    </header>

  
    <div class="entry-summary" style="text-indent: 100%; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden;">
      <p>Estimates suggest more than two million people worldwide would benefit from an organ transplant. While the donation rates vary greatly between countries, the contrast between the increasing numbers of…</p>
    </div>

  <aside id="meta" class="grid-four">
    
