      <article class="article">
   :36:06Z" datetime="2012-02-19T19:36:06Z" itemprop="datePublished" pubdate="pubdate">February 19 2012</time>
          Five myths about organ donation in&nbsp;Australia
</a>      </article>
  </section>


          
              <div class="related-articles blockset blocks-1x1-vertical grid-last">
    <h4>Related articles</h4>

    <div class="blocks-1x1 slammed grid-last">
      
<article data-id="31270" class="clearfix placed analysis published">
    <figure>
      <a class="article-link" href="/more-people-can-donate-tissue-than-organs-so-why-do-we-know-so-little-about-it-31270">
        <img alt="" data-echo="https://62e528761d0685343e1c-f3d1b99a743ffa4142d9d7f1978d9686.ssl.cf2.rackcdn.com/files/58240/width324x324/kbv72n8j-1409825420.jpg" data-id="58240" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" />
</a>        <figcaption>
            <span class="caption">
              Eyes – windows on the soul?
            </span>
            <span class="source" title="Source">Ángelo González</span>
        </figcaption>
    </figure>

  <header>



    <h2><a href="/more-people-can-donate-tissue-than-organs-so-why-do-we-know-so-little-about-it-31270">More people can donate tissue than organs – so why do we know so little about&nbsp;it?</a></h2>
      <p class="byline">
        <span><span>By </span><a href="http://thecon-people-can-donate-tissue-than-organs-so-why-do-we-know-so-little-about-it-31270">More people can donate tissue than organs – so why do we know so little abversation.com/profiles/tracy-long-sutehall-137037">Tracy Long-Sutehall</a><em>, University of Southampton</em></span>
      </p>
  </header>

</article>

